      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal similarity analysis demonstrating that simulation input parameters (Reynolds number, Stokes number, exposure time distribution) match experimental conditions within defined equivalency bounds.",
      "rationale": "No formal similarity analysis performed. Reynolds number matching verified informally; Stokes number and Lagrangian exposure time distributions not compared between simulation and experiment. Factor not-assessed at MRL 5."
